  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1236707/" class="title-link">《可怕的科学》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1236707"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/bingdian/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1616152-95.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bingdian/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">viRRoR</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-11-09"
      class="main-meta">2007-11-09 17:27:48</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1236707_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      《可怕的科学》是我很喜欢的一套书，每次看这本书都如痴如醉，的确，科学并不可怕，可怕的是枯燥的表达，这是这本书的作者说的，对此我深表同感，我们学校也有科学课，但是总是没有看《可怕的科学》好玩。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1236707/#comments">(3回应)</a>
